P(C=T|X=T, D=T)
...    =F,  =T
...    =T,  =F

P(C, X, D) = P(C)*P(X|C)*P(D|C,X)
           = P(C)*P(X|C)*P(D|C)
           = P(C) * 0.9 * 0.65
           = 0.101 * 0.9 * 0.65
           = 0.059085

P(C) = P(C|P,S)+P(C|!P,!S)+P(C|P,!S)+P(C|!P,S)
     = 0.05 + 0.001 + 0.02 + 0.03 = 0.101

P(C, !X, D) = 0.101 * 0.2 * 0.65 = 0.01313
P(C, X, !D) = 0.101 * 0.9 * 0.3 = 0.02727

